         <div class="highlight"> 
          <div class="highlight-text-container float-right"> 
           <div class="highlight-text"> <span class="icon highlight-icon"> 
             <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewbox="0 0 48 48" fill="none"> <path d="M39.0145 28.9799C40.2818 26.6004 41 23.8841 41 21C41 11.6112 33.3888 4 24 4C14.6112 4 7 11.6112 7 21C7 24.0964 7.82785 26.9995 9.2743 29.5C9.29757 29.5402 9.32099 29.5803 9.34458 29.6204C9.83118 30.4458 10.3855 31.2266 11 31.955C11.0001 31.9551 10.9999 31.955 11 31.955C11.0069 31.9632 11.014 31.9716 11.0209 31.9798C11.0265 31.9864 11.0325 31.9935 11.0381 32H11L21.0884 42.7093C22.6675 44.3856 25.3324 44.3856 26.9115 42.7093L37 32H36.9619C36.9673 31.9937 36.9726 31.9874 36.978 31.9811L36.9788 31.9801L36.9795 31.9792C37.0522 31.8934 37.1241 31.8068 37.1951 31.7195C37.7614 31.0232 38.2738 30.2813 38.7257 29.5C38.8249 29.3285 38.9212 29.1551 39.0145 28.9799ZM24.0049 27.5C20.6912 27.5 18.0049 24.8137 18.0049 21.5C18.0049 18.1863 20.6912 15.5 24.0049 15.5C27.3186 15.5 30.0049 18.1863 30.0049 21.5C30.0049 24.8137 27.3186 27.5 24.0049 27.5Z"></path> 
             </svg> </span> 
            <h3 class="highlight-text__header"> Pick up where you left off </h3> 
            <p class="highlight-text__subheader"> Microsoft 365 seamlessly tracks updates, task, and comments across all your files so you can pick up right where you left off </p> 
           </div> 
          </div> 
          <div class="highlight-image__container"> 
           <img class="highlight-image float-left" src="https://res.cdn.office.net/officehub/images/content/images/unauth-refresh/highlight-commercial-4-b66ce988de.png" alt="Screenshot showing recommended actions on recently updated files"> 
          </div> 
         </div> 
         <div class="highlight more-apps"> 
          <div class="highlight-text-container highlight-text-container--more-apps"> 
           <div class="highlight-text"> 
            <h3 class="highlight-text__header"> More apps in fewer places </h3> 
            <p class="highlight-text__subheader"> The new Microsoft 365 brings together your favorite Microsoft apps all in one, intuitive platform </p> 
           </div> 
          </div> 
          <img class="highlight-image more-apps-image" src="https://res.cdn.office.net/officehub/images/content/images/unauth-refresh/more-apps-commercial-620d899e6a.png" alt="Puzzle illustration showing the interconnectedness of applications within Microsoft 365"> 
         </div> 
        </div> 
        <div id="unauth-tab-content-edu" class="tab-content is-hidden" style="display: none" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="unauth-tab-edu"> 
         <h2 class="tab-header"> Empower your students and teachers to achieve more </h2> 
         <p class="tab-subheader"> Teachers and students get access to the best tools for learning anywhere—in the classroom, remotely or in a blended environment—for free </p> 
         <img class="tab-header-image" src="https://res.cdn.office.net/officehub/images/content/images/unauth-refresh/m365-rebrand-value-edu-8f1caf2f3b.png" alt="Visual representation of students and educators connected through Microsoft 365"> 
         <div class="highlight"> 
          <div class="highlight-text-container float-left"> 
           <div class="highlight-text"> <span class="icon highlight-icon"> 
             <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewbox="0 0 48 48" fill="none"> <path d="M31.605 6.83811C31.2415 6.49733 30.7103 6.40497 30.2531 6.60304C29.7959 6.80111 29.5 7.25178 29.5 7.75003V13.2223C29.1425 13.2305 28.7251 13.2514 28.26 13.2944C26.725 13.4362 24.6437 13.8204 22.4841 14.799C18.0824 16.7935 13.5579 21.1728 12.5081 30.3581C12.4493 30.8729 12.7141 31.3706 13.174 31.6094C13.6338 31.8482 14.1932 31.7785 14.5805 31.4343C18.9164 27.5801 22.9778 25.9209 25.9168 25.2155C27.3897 24.862 28.5872 24.7466 29.4032 24.718C29.4361 24.7169 29.4684 24.7158 29.5 24.715V30.25C29.5 30.7483 29.7959 31.1989 30.2531 31.397C30.7103 31.5951 31.2415 31.5027 31.605 31.162L43.605 19.9119C43.857 19.6756 44 19.3455 44 19C44 18.6545 43.857 18.3244 43.605 18.0881L31.605 6.83811ZM6 14.25C6 10.7983 8.79822 8.00003 12.25 8.00003H20.5C21.1904 8.00003 21.75 8.55967 21.75 9.25003C21.75 9.94039 21.1904 10.5 20.5 10.5H12.25C10.1789 10.5 8.5 12.179 8.5 14.25V35.75C8.5 37.8211 10.1789 39.5 12.25 39.5H33.75C35.8211 39.5 37.5 37.8211 37.5 35.75V33.5C37.5 32.8097 38.0596 32.25 38.75 32.25C39.4404 32.25 40 32.8097 40 33.5V35.75C40 39.2018 37.2018 42 33.75 42H12.25C8.79822 42 6 39.2018 6 35.75V14.25Z"></path> 
