            <h3 class="highlight-text__header"> Create anywhere, anytime, with any app </h3> 
            <p class="highlight-text__subheader"> Spark creativity and collaboration in any learning environment—whether in the classroom, remote, or blended—with intuitive, inclusive design </p> 
           </div> 
          </div> 
          <div class="highlight-image__container float-right"> 
           <img class="highlight-image float-right" src="https://res.cdn.office.net/officehub/images/content/images/unauth-refresh/highlight-edu-1-6f56908e42.png" alt="Create tiles demonstrating some of the free create possibilities with Microsoft 365"> 
          </div> 
         </div> 
         <div class="highlight"> 
          <div class="highlight-text-container float-right"> 
           <div class="highlight-text"> <span class="icon highlight-icon"> 
             <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewbox="0 0 48 48" fill="none"> <path d="M38.9994 7.25C38.9994 6.55964 38.4398 6 37.7494 6C37.0591 6 36.4994 6.55964 36.4994 7.25V9H34.7494C34.0591 9 33.4994 9.55964 33.4994 10.25C33.4994 10.9404 34.0591 11.5 34.7494 11.5H36.4994V13.25C36.4994 13.9404 37.0591 14.5 37.7494 14.5C38.4398 14.5 38.9994 13.9404 38.9994 13.25V11.5H40.7494C41.4398 11.5 41.9994 10.9404 41.9994 10.25C41.9994 9.55964 41.4398 9 40.7494 9H38.9994V7.25ZM14.9994 11.25C14.9994 10.5596 14.4398 10 13.7494 10C13.0591 10 12.4994 10.5596 12.4994 11.25V13H10.7494C10.0591 13 9.49944 13.5596 9.49944 14.25C9.49944 14.9404 10.0591 15.5 10.7494 15.5H12.4994V17.25C12.4994 17.9404 13.0591 18.5 13.7494 18.5C14.4398 18.5 14.9994 17.9404 14.9994 17.25V15.5H16.7494C17.4398 15.5 17.9994 14.9404 17.9994 14.25C17.9994 13.5596 17.4398 13 16.7494 13H14.9994V11.25ZM33.7494 30C34.4398 30 34.9994 30.5596 34.9994 31.25V33H36.7494C37.4398 33 37.9994 33.5596 37.9994 34.25C37.9994 34.9404 37.4398 35.5 36.7494 35.5H34.9994V37.25C34.9994 37.9404 34.4398 38.5 33.7494 38.5C33.0591 38.5 32.4994 37.9404 32.4994 37.25V35.5H30.7494C30.0591 35.5 29.4994 34.9404 29.4994 34.25C29.4994 33.5596 30.0591 33 30.7494 33H32.4994V31.25C32.4994 30.5596 33.0591 30 33.7494 30ZM32.6065 15.4044C30.7515 13.5494 27.744 13.5494 25.889 15.4044L24.5304 16.763L31.2479 23.4805L32.6065 22.1219C34.4615 20.2669 34.4615 17.2594 32.6065 15.4044ZM29.4801 25.2483L22.7626 18.5308L5.39515 35.8982C3.54016 37.7532 3.54016 40.7608 5.39515 42.6158C7.25014 44.4707 10.2577 44.4707 12.1127 42.6158L29.4801 25.2483Z"></path> 
