            <h3 class="highlight-text__header"> Empower your educators </h3> 
            <p class="highlight-text__subheader"> Create equitable learning environments that help students develop knowledge and skills essential for both academic and career success </p> 
           </div> 
          </div> 
          <div class="highlight-image__container"> 
           <img class="highlight-image float-left" src="https://res.cdn.office.net/officehub/images/content/images/unauth-refresh/highlight-edu-2-a65339870b.png" alt="Screenshot depicting lesson plans and recorded class sessions within Microsoft 365"> 
          </div> 
         </div> 
         <div class="highlight"> 
